{"tid":2005204,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[立場訪問] 極政治化時代之下，我們還需要「香港電影」嗎？","createTime":"2020-05-07T03:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T12:46:42.000Z","uid":15213,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1d34b6f022cb2b0381313e8f245691a9d3f40c","tid":2005204,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"這時代，各區曾經每個週末都發生流血衝突，原來人來人往的假日電影院變得疏落，若無其事地看戲成為了「港豬」的表現。<br />\n<br />\n這時代，內地影片平台要求香港或台灣演員簽署合約，保證10年內不會因政治取向遭大陸封殺。<br />\n<br />\n這時代，觀眾進場前要仔細審查演員、導演、幕後人員的政治立場，根據其「黃藍」程度，才能決定是否能安心入場觀看。<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n就連 38 年來一直處在鎂光燈焦點、充滿天王巨星及各種情緒的金像獎頒獎典禮，也敵不過全球疫情，首次改成在星期三的中午 3 點於網上直播舉行，由金像獎協會主席爾冬陞花了十分鐘宣讀得獎名單後，便淡然結束。直播期間，留言區亦依舊充斥了「光復香港，時代革命」等等抗爭口號，還有指責香港金像獎不應讓《少年的你》這類「大陸戲」成為大贏家的留言。<br />\n<br />\n毫無疑問，香港進入了一個政治主導生活的時代，當食飯、買衫、交通都要取決於政見時，電影自然亦不能例外。對於「香港電影」的新角色，不同電影人各有不同的感悟。適逢金像獎頒獎禮舉行，《立場新聞》訪問提名今屆最佳導演的《十年》及《幻愛》導演周冠威、首次提名最佳男配角的盧鎮業、演藝學院電視電影學院前院長舒琪、「社區院線」創辦人之一的張景暉，探討「香港電影」在社運年代之中，到底應是娛樂，是文化載體，還是抗爭工具？以往掙扎求存多年的電影人，在亂世又該如何自處？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E7%89%B9%E5%AF%AB-%E6%A5%B5%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%96%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E9%82%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E5%97%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258C%2596%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E9%2582%2584%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E5%2597%258E%2F&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=d11951fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25AF%25AB-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258C%2596%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E9%2582%2584%25E9%259C%2580%25E8%25A6%2581-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E5%2597%258E%2F&h=0d463231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E7%89%B9%E5%AF%AB-%E6%A5%B5%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%8C%96%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%8B-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E9%82%84%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E5%97%8E/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家一定要懲罰真正港產片"},{"pid":"3e7885eacf48bb461449e381109262b6d01efbcb","tid":2005204,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8fac5e5a01e59e47f6cf9f170d3d44209bb8a8","tid":2005204,"uid":219010,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"香港電影不再係香港 電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edccb4e3c76ce7d4f9ef9718fe03a5ee65455165","tid":2005204,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"藍嘅，唔睇<br />\n黃嘅，無卡士，題材冷門，悶，搵唔到有得睇嘅戲院..........都係唔睇"},{"pid":"92e3b9439337a8c0aa6d3e58b994b36e1143b7d7","tid":2005204,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"其實已經冇需要,  早前大陸話唔會再用香港藝員, 班某利先識得返唻做返D疇, COLLECT SKIN 啦"},{"pid":"98a413acd9636aeff9a399d6c74acdcd4a7b4ecc","tid":2005204,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T12: